    <item>
      <title>停火开始后以色列与哈马斯交换人质和囚犯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-19/first-three-israeli-hostages-released-in-gaza-under-ceasefire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈马斯周日释放了三名人质，以换取关押在以色列监狱的 90 名巴勒斯坦人，加沙战争长期推迟的停火开始生效。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-19/first-three-israeli-hostages-released-in-gaza-under-ceasefire</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 19 Jan 2025 15:24:06 GMT</pubDate>
